column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name],     p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.petromag_r, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, p.colc_u, p.rowc_u, p.colc_g, p.rowc_g, p.colc_r, p.rowc_r, p.colc_i, p.rowc_i, p.colc_z, p.rowc_z, c.stripe, c.skyversion, c.startMu, p.deVRad_g, p.deVRad_r, p.deVRad_i, p.deVRad_z, p.deVAB_r, p.deVAB_i, p.deVAB_z FROM #upload u       JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id       JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON p.objID = x.objID       JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID       JOIN Field as f ON p.fieldid=f.fieldid       JOIN Segment as g ON f.segmentid=g.segmentid        JOIN Chunk as c ON g.chunkid=c.chunkid ORDER by x.up_id
